headline: Goldman Sachs Begins Coverage of Analog Devices (ADI) Stock, Gives Buy
summary: Analog Devices, Inc. (NASDAQ:ADI) is one of the Most Promising AI Stocks to Buy Now. Goldman Sachs initiated coverage of the company’s stock with a “Buy” rating and a price objective of $285, as reported by The Fly. The firm initiated the US analog and radio frequency semiconductor sector with a relatively bullish outlook, noting the cyclical opportunities it expects. […]
